ABSTRACT
A system and method for retrieving contact information
based on image recognition searches is disclosed. A
requestor takes a picture of a user or retrieves a storage
image of a user and transmits the image to an image
recognition module. The image recognition module identi-
fies the user and determines whether the requestor can
receive access to the user's contact information based on
permission rules. For example, the permission rule includes
a requirement that the user and the requestor be sufficiently
related on a social graph generated by a social network
application. The permission rules can also include a require-
ment that the requestor have a predetermined proximity to
the image. Once the permission rules are satisfied, the image
recognition module transmits the user's contact information
to the requestor.
